Cops do that, you know?

30:09.708 --> 30:11.141
- Well, you could
have just said that,

30:11.143 --> 30:14.077
and made this whole
thing a lot easier.

30:14.079 --> 30:16.747
- Yeah, well it seemed
pretty from over here.

30:16.749 --> 30:18.448
Looked like you'd
done it before.

30:18.450 --> 30:19.249
- No.

30:19.251 --> 30:20.150
No.

30:20.152 --> 30:21.073
- Calm yourself.

30:25.423 --> 30:26.156
Sit down.

30:26.158 --> 30:27.038
Take a seat.

30:31.830 --> 30:36.066
So, what is it
you want me doing?

30:39.204 --> 30:43.207
- Um... well, I got
this brother in law.

30:43.209 --> 30:44.541
- Yep.

30:44.543 --> 30:46.410
- He's... he's a bad guy.

30:46.412 --> 30:47.611
I mean, really bad.

30:47.613 --> 30:50.380
He... he beat sup on my sister.

30:50.382 --> 30:51.715
- Yep.

30:51.717 --> 30:53.837
- I mean, the other day
he almost killed her.

30:56.521 --> 30:58.455
- So, what do you want me to do?

31:02.160 --> 31:05.562
- Well, I was wondering
if... you know,

31:05.564 --> 31:09.066
you... you could
take care of him?

31:11.703 --> 31:14.338
- Oh.

31:14.340 --> 31:16.139
You want me to kill him.

31:20.144 --> 31:22.546
- Yeah, well, I would like
to talk more about that.

31:26.918 --> 31:30.454
- How much money you
got on this, again?

31:30.456 --> 31:33.190
- Um... $2,000.

31:33.192 --> 31:34.032
Back home.

31:37.829 --> 31:40.264
- Well, let's go get it.

31:40.266 --> 31:43.700
I mean, maybe we can
discuss it a little more,

31:43.702 --> 31:45.802
if... if that's OK.

31:45.804 --> 31:46.837
- Sure.

31:46.839 --> 31:48.305
We can talk about it in the car.

31:48.307 --> 31:50.774
Girlfriend, and she says...

31:50.776 --> 31:52.809
she says, how did you know?

31:52.811 --> 31:54.912
All I did was drink
iced tea all night,

31:54.914 --> 31:56.747
and he didn't hit me once.

31:56.749 --> 31:59.149
And the girlfriend
says, she says...

31:59.151 --> 32:02.719
says that that's what happens
when you keep your mouth shut.

32:02.721 --> 32:03.481
Right?

32:08.059 --> 32:12.462
You ain't thinking that's funny
cause of your sister, I guess.

32:12.464 --> 32:15.699
Well, some people
got a sense of humor.

32:15.701 --> 32:17.167
- Sorry.

32:17.169 --> 32:21.905
Uh... so how long you been
doing this kind of thing?

32:21.907 --> 32:22.739
- What thing?

32:22.741 --> 32:25.375
The killing thing?

32:25.377 --> 32:27.911
- Well, a while.

32:27.913 --> 32:32.582
But it ain't exactly
full time, you know?

32:32.584 --> 32:35.585
It's hard telling how many
fellas want a man dead enough

32:35.587 --> 32:39.022
to pay for it, but not
enough to do it themselves.

32:39.024 --> 32:41.425
- And you've done this...
you've done this kind of thing

32:41.427 --> 32:42.292
before, right?

32:42.294 --> 32:44.261
For... for money?

32:44.263 --> 32:46.530
- Oh, sure.

32:46.532 --> 32:51.668
- So, how do we... how
do you go about it?

32:51.670 --> 32:56.139
- Well, you... you give me your
money, I shoot him in his head.

32:56.141 --> 32:58.141
Ain't like I'm teaching
Portuguese, or anything.

32:58.143 --> 33:01.812
- No, I just, mean, you
know, why do most people

33:01.814 --> 33:03.847
want to do something like this?

33:03.849 --> 33:05.415
- Jesus Christ.

33:05.417 --> 33:07.777
You keep nipping at my heels,
you're gonna buy me dinner.

33:11.323 --> 33:14.157
- Those motel walls
were so thin, all

33:14.159 --> 33:18.662
I was hearing for a week was...
And he's

33:18.664 --> 33:19.963
wanting to bust
his nuts, so he's

33:19.965 --> 33:22.833
like... you know how that is?

33:22.835 --> 33:24.468
Oh yeah, baby.

33:24.470 --> 33:25.736
For a week, man.

33:25.738 --> 33:28.872
I'm telling you,
it drove me crazy.

33:28.874 --> 33:31.141
These burgers are
fucking fantastic, man.

33:31.143 --> 33:32.676
I'm... I'm impressed.

33:35.513 --> 33:38.081
Mm.

33:38.083 --> 33:40.250
- So what do you like
to do in Mississippi?

33:40.252 --> 33:45.022
- Well, I keep myself
company just fine.

33:45.024 --> 33:48.225
- Are you from there?

33:48.227 --> 33:50.627
- Mm-mm.

33:50.629 --> 33:52.629
Mm.

33:52.631 --> 33:53.764
Born in Utah.

33:53.766 --> 33:54.664
Come out here about...

33:54.666 --> 33:56.700
- He's a terrible man.

33:56.702 --> 33:59.369
- You said that.

33:59.371 --> 34:02.339
- I wish I could
just do it myself.

34:02.341 --> 34:03.940
- Yeah.

34:03.942 --> 34:05.776
- I mean, that's moral, right?

34:05.778 --> 34:09.746
If it saves my sister, and... and
he goes off somewhere better?

34:09.748 --> 34:11.348
- Refill?

34:11.350 --> 34:13.216
- And the check, please.

34:13.217 --> 34:15.138
- I'll get that
right for you, hun.

34:18.056 --> 34:19.790
- How do you square
yourself off with God

34:19.792 --> 34:22.559
with something like this?

34:22.561 --> 34:24.527
- Seriously?

34:24.530 --> 34:28.197
- Son, if you hadn't figured
out that this stuff was

34:28.199 --> 34:32.235
bullshit by the time you reached
puberty, I got nothing for you.

34:32.237 --> 34:34.036
- What, you don't believe in God?

34:34.039 --> 34:35.605
Well, what the fuck
are you saying?

34:35.607 --> 34:38.675
We just die, and that's it?

34:38.677 --> 34:40.177
I couldn't live like that.

34:40.179 --> 34:42.012
- Well, that's great, but it
just exists in your head.

34:42.014 --> 34:44.947
Ain't none of my business.

34:44.949 --> 34:47.851
- I mean, I got my thoughts,
and you have yours, you know?

34:47.853 --> 34:49.186
Who knows, right?

34:49.188 --> 34:53.322
So I just... I just want
my sister to be happy.

34:53.324 --> 34:55.358
- Well, whether it's your
religion or your sister,

34:55.360 --> 34:57.461
you tell me what you
hold close, and I'll

34:57.463 --> 35:00.063
tell you where you're
lying to yourself.

35:00.065 --> 35:03.700
You be careful, boy.

35:03.702 --> 35:05.035
What are you looking at?

35:05.037 --> 35:05.735
- What?

35:05.737 --> 35:06.538
- Not you.

35:08.806 --> 35:11.274
You've been looking over here
for the past five minutes.

35:11.276 --> 35:12.609
You want to tell me why?

35:12.611 --> 35:15.045
- I don't like the way
you talk about religion.

35:15.047 --> 35:19.015
Maybe you want to shut up.

35:19.017 --> 35:22.419
- I don't give a good
god damn what you like.

35:22.421 --> 35:24.421
You better put those eyes
back in that soup boy,

35:24.423 --> 35:26.089
or you ain't gonna
have much use for 'em.

35:26.091 --> 35:28.011
- I'll look wherever
I want to look.

35:32.296 --> 35:33.697
- Yep.

35:33.699 --> 35:34.739
I guess you're gonna.

35:39.070 --> 35:42.973
- Look, maybe I made a
big mistake with this.

35:42.975 --> 35:44.274
- What?

35:44.276 --> 35:45.342
- Maybe I can just drive
you back home, and...

35:45.344 --> 35:46.476
- What, cause of that?

35:46.478 --> 35:48.145
- No, I'm just, you
know, thinking...

35:48.147 --> 35:50.388
- Why don't you go outside
and bring the car around?

35:53.284 --> 35:54.351
- We gotta wait for...

35:54.353 --> 35:55.986
- No, I'll take care of that.

35:55.988 --> 35:57.787
She'll bring it, we'll
square it up later.

35:57.789 --> 35:58.622
You go and get the car.

35:58.624 --> 36:02.626
- I'll meet you outside.

36:02.628 --> 36:04.027
- Oh.

36:04.029 --> 36:04.710
OK.

36:30.923 --> 36:33.823
- Get In the car.

36:33.825 --> 36:35.458
I didn't see you come out.

36:42.099 --> 36:43.466
- I got kids.

36:45.170 --> 36:46.336
- Oh, shit.

36:48.973 --> 36:49.906
- Hey.

36:49.908 --> 36:50.640
Hey.

36:50.642 --> 36:52.108
Look at me!

36:52.110 --> 36:53.243
Get in the car.

36:59.617 --> 37:01.017
No, no, no, no.

37:01.019 --> 37:01.618
No, no.

37:01.620 --> 37:03.019
Hey!

37:03.021 --> 37:04.020
Come here!

37:04.022 --> 37:05.488
You get in the car.

37:05.490 --> 37:07.023
You wanna talk about this,
we'll talk about it later.

37:07.025 --> 37:07.946
Get in the car!

37:38.389 --> 37:41.358
- Hey, you look... you look great.

37:41.360 --> 37:43.827
I got... I got you these.

37:43.829 --> 37:45.795
- Thanks.

37:45.797 --> 37:46.598
Come in.

38:26.604 --> 38:28.271
- Tastes good.

38:28.273 --> 38:31.508
- You've had it before.

38:31.510 --> 38:32.942
- Yeah, I know... I know.

38:32.944 --> 38:37.714
It's just... tastes like you
did something different.

38:37.716 --> 38:38.596
- Little bit.

38:42.420 --> 38:46.523
- Well, what'd you do?

38:46.525 --> 38:49.659
- It's just a new recipe.

38:49.661 --> 38:52.062
- Oh.

38:52.064 --> 38:58.234
Well, yeah, it's...
it's interesting.

38:58.236 --> 38:59.037
- Thanks.

39:05.443 --> 39:09.646
- Was it a recipe
with poison in it?

39:09.648 --> 39:12.349
I mean, it's like,
really, really bad.

39:12.351 --> 39:13.950
- It's not good.

39:13.952 --> 39:14.751
I'm sorry.

39:14.753 --> 39:15.652
- No, no.

39:15.654 --> 39:16.653
No, you tried.

39:16.655 --> 39:19.022
It's just... wow.

39:19.024 --> 39:20.757
Don't you work in a restaurant?

39:20.759 --> 39:23.093
Now you don't get to finish.

39:23.095 --> 39:23.827
- No.

39:23.829 --> 39:25.195
Wait, wait.

39:25.197 --> 39:25.929
I'm... I'm eating.

39:25.931 --> 39:26.529
I'm eating.

39:26.531 --> 39:28.098
Now I'm embarrassed.

39:28.100 --> 39:29.199
Never cooking again.

39:29.201 --> 39:31.234
- That might be smart.

39:31.236 --> 39:32.168
- OK.

39:32.170 --> 39:33.069
Now you're done.

39:33.071 --> 39:33.831
- Wait.

39:36.307 --> 39:38.541
- It's all right.

39:38.543 --> 39:40.243
I'm not going to hurt you.

39:40.245 --> 39:41.046
- I know.

39:46.484 --> 39:51.855
- I don't remember
the other night.

39:51.857 --> 39:53.156
You know that, right?

39:53.158 --> 39:54.891
I'm not saying that makes it OK.

39:54.893 --> 39:55.773
- It doesn't.

39:59.029 --> 40:00.964
- But it wasn't me.

40:00.966 --> 40:04.000
Do you know what I mean?

40:04.002 --> 40:04.934
- Yes it was.

40:08.239 --> 40:11.608
So don't forget that.

40:11.610 --> 40:13.943
Wait.

40:13.945 --> 40:14.866
I can do that.

40:18.315 --> 40:19.075
- Sure.

40:34.365 --> 40:36.166
- So you got any chores
that need doing?

40:36.168 --> 40:38.701
Can I swing by tomorrow?

40:38.703 --> 40:41.604
- I'll think of something.

40:41.606 --> 40:42.366
- Great.

40:45.242 --> 40:45.962
Hey.

40:46.812 --> 40:48.445
I'm sorry.

40:48.447 --> 40:49.212
I didn't mean to
make you nervous.

40:49.214 --> 40:49.979
- It's not that.

40:49.981 --> 40:52.982
It...

40:52.984 --> 40:53.983
- Well, what?

40:53.985 --> 40:54.751
What?

40:54.753 --> 40:55.952
- It just hurts.

41:05.696 --> 41:10.834
What are you... what
are you... what are you...

41:10.836 --> 41:13.636
what are you doing
with someone like me?

41:13.638 --> 41:15.038
Have you lost your mind?

41:15.040 --> 41:15.939
- What are you saying?

41:15.941 --> 41:20.210
I... if I saw that on anyone
else, I'd tell them to leave.

41:20.212 --> 41:21.778
- So what, you're
going to leave me?

41:21.780 --> 41:23.379
That's not... that's not what...

41:23.381 --> 41:24.414
- Yeah.

41:24.416 --> 41:25.582
Cause you signed on for this.

41:25.584 --> 41:26.649
You don't get to
make that decision.

41:26.651 --> 41:27.784
I already left you.

41:27.786 --> 41:29.519
- No.

41:29.521 --> 41:35.225
I... I love you so much,
and you did this to me.

41:35.227 --> 41:35.925
- I'm sorry.

41:35.927 --> 41:37.360
- No.

41:37.362 --> 41:39.829
You... you wanted to fix this.

41:39.831 --> 41:41.931
So you're going to go
home to wherever the hell

41:41.933 --> 41:44.400
you're staying, and
you're going to come back

41:44.402 --> 41:46.936
here tomorrow and
make it up to me.

41:46.938 --> 41:48.705
And you're going to
do that the next day,

41:48.707 --> 41:50.373
and every day after
that, and forever.

41:50.375 --> 41:51.056
OK?

41:53.911 --> 41:54.671
- Yeah.

42:00.150 --> 42:01.551
- Just go home.

42:01.553 --> 42:03.152
I'll see you tomorrow.

42:28.879 --> 42:32.081
Want to listen to the radio?

42:32.083 --> 42:33.483
- Naw.

42:33.485 --> 42:35.418
Think I'll just... I kind
of want to just get home.

42:35.420 --> 42:37.620
- Well, that's
where we are going.

42:41.792 --> 42:43.927
- Look, we never
really agreed to a...

42:43.929 --> 42:45.662
- I'm not leaving my
house in the middle

42:45.664 --> 42:46.896
of the night for nothing.

42:49.166 --> 42:52.835
- Well, I think I said I kind
of want to just talk about it.

42:52.837 --> 42:54.804
- We were talking
about how, not if.

42:54.806 --> 42:56.606
You'd best understand that.

43:01.345 --> 43:03.913
They don't know
what we're driving.

43:03.915 --> 43:05.748
And when they find
them bodies, they

43:05.750 --> 43:07.717
ain't gonna piece
anything together.

43:07.719 --> 43:12.855
They'll just be running around
like retards at the rodeo.

43:12.857 --> 43:16.559
Um, do you think that
maybe we could, you know,

43:16.561 --> 43:19.195
stay at a motel for the night?

43:19.197 --> 43:21.197
- I can drive till daybreak.

43:21.199 --> 43:23.319
- Yeah, well I kind of
want to crash in a bed.

43:26.303 --> 43:29.606
- Well, I guess every man
ain't cut out for the road.

43:40.250 --> 43:41.217
- All right.

43:41.219 --> 43:43.786
I'm gonna crash out.

43:43.788 --> 43:46.556
- Yeah, you had
yourself quite a night.

43:46.558 --> 43:48.858
Get yourself some sleep, there.

43:48.860 --> 43:49.580
- Yep.

43:52.363 --> 43:54.631
- Take a shower.

43:54.633 --> 43:56.673
Wash that shit off
the top of your lip.

43:59.036 --> 44:01.404
What time do you want to
hit the road in the morning?

44:04.575 --> 44:07.343
About 10:00.

44:07.345 --> 44:08.111
10:00 it is.

44:11.015 --> 44:12.348
- All right.

44:12.350 --> 44:13.230
See ya then.

44:19.024 --> 44:22.358
- I'm gonna need that phone.

44:22.360 --> 44:24.761
- Well, I don't
think you can just...

44:24.763 --> 44:27.230
- You gonna give it to me, or
you gonna make me come over

44:27.232 --> 44:27.997
and get it?

44:27.999 --> 44:28.879
Come on, now.

44:37.074 --> 44:38.007
Your cell, too.

44:40.477 --> 44:42.245
- It doesn't even
get reception here.

44:42.247 --> 44:43.146
- Well, lucky you.

44:43.148 --> 44:44.229
You won't even miss it.

45:02.733 --> 45:03.766
Get you some sleep.

45:10.474 --> 45:12.041
Try not to keep
yourself up thinking

45:12.043 --> 45:14.410
about all the people
done screwed on that bed.

45:58.622 --> 45:59.889
Enjoying the evening?

46:02.626 --> 46:05.561
- Can't sleep.

46:05.563 --> 46:09.232
- Wanna go curb
crawling, or something?

46:09.234 --> 46:10.233
I don't.

46:13.203 --> 46:14.403
- Then go back to sleep.

46:29.686 --> 46:30.453
10:00 AM.

46:30.455 --> 46:31.554
Time to get up.

46:36.026 --> 46:36.793
- What?

46:36.795 --> 46:37.927
It's 10:00.

46:37.929 --> 46:41.364
Time to hit the road.

46:41.366 --> 46:42.765
- OK.

46:42.767 --> 46:43.633
All right.

46:43.635 --> 46:46.302
- Gordon.

46:46.304 --> 46:48.337
- What?

46:48.339 --> 46:52.108
- I've spent my whole life
hand holding people like you.

46:52.110 --> 46:57.980
But you... you don't know
me at all, and that's fine.

46:57.982 --> 46:59.649
Hell, I might even
take comfort in that,

46:59.651 --> 47:04.453
but you best keep that in mind
before you do something stupid.

47:04.455 --> 47:07.690
Now, we're gonna
go to your house

47:07.692 --> 47:10.059
and do what you need done.

47:10.061 --> 47:12.929
Or you could just pay me the
money, and I'll be on my way.

47:12.931 --> 47:16.032
Either way, I don't care.

47:16.034 --> 47:19.635
But you're never going to
be a man in your own mind

47:19.637 --> 47:21.737
unless this thing is finished.

47:21.739 --> 47:24.974
And you ain't doing it yourself.

47:24.976 --> 47:28.744
Now, it sounds like
she ain't leaving him.

47:28.746 --> 47:31.914
And he sure ain't leaving her.

47:31.916 --> 47:34.951
So it's up to you.

47:34.953 --> 47:37.920
All you've got in
your life is choices.

47:37.922 --> 47:39.155
What's yours going to be?

47:45.662 --> 47:48.798
- I want him dead.

47:48.800 --> 47:51.567
- All right.

47:51.569 --> 47:52.435
Get yourself dressed.

47:52.437 --> 47:53.437
See you in the car.

47:56.240 --> 47:57.120
- Hey, Howard?

47:59.142 --> 48:02.311
Can you, uh, just do
me a favor, and not

48:02.313 --> 48:06.115
kill anyone else
until we get there?

48:06.117 --> 48:08.784
- Gordon, I don't think that's
a promise I could comfortably

48:08.786 --> 48:10.086
keep.

48:10.088 --> 48:13.756
Especially if you keep
running your mouth.

48:13.758 --> 48:15.458
See you outside in five.

48:40.817 --> 48:41.817
- Hey.

48:41.819 --> 48:42.539
- Hey.

48:54.431 --> 48:57.633
- That Auburn, you say?

48:57.635 --> 48:59.969
- Yep.

48:59.971 --> 49:03.005
- That's pretty much
Penntucky, isn't it?

49:03.007 --> 49:05.241
How cold it get up there?

49:05.243 --> 49:06.042
- I don't know.

49:06.044 --> 49:07.543
Pretty cold, I guess.

49:07.545 --> 49:10.413
- God damn, that's gonna do
my joins in something awful.

49:10.415 --> 49:13.582
- So what's... what's the plan for
keeping this whole thing quiet?

49:13.584 --> 49:15.584
- What's the worry, kid?

49:15.586 --> 49:16.986
- I don't know.

49:16.988 --> 49:18.854
What would happen if, you
know, you got arrested?

49:18.856 --> 49:21.757
- Why would I get arrested?

49:21.759 --> 49:22.892
- I don't know.

49:22.894 --> 49:23.659
You've been caught
before, right?

49:23.661 --> 49:24.994
- Jesus Christ.

49:24.996 --> 49:25.594
Do you want to see my
resume, or something?

49:25.596 --> 49:26.996
- No.

49:26.998 --> 49:28.197
I just know you went to
prison before, so I just...

49:28.199 --> 49:29.398
- Too chicken shit
to do it yourself.

49:29.400 --> 49:31.100
How about this?

49:31.102 --> 49:32.668
I want you money, so
I'm gonna warn you...

49:32.670 --> 49:37.139
you keep talking like this,
I'll shoot you in the mouth.

49:37.141 --> 49:38.975
I'm sorry.

49:38.977 --> 49:40.142
- If you knew how much
I felt like putting you

49:40.144 --> 49:42.064
down right now,
you'd keep it shut.

50:05.702 --> 50:06.769
- I'm gonna get a lemonade.

50:06.771 --> 50:08.904
You want one?

50:08.906 --> 50:10.406
- A lemonade?

50:10.408 --> 50:11.841
- Yeah.

50:11.843 --> 50:13.376
