lands on all fours,

56:17.575 --> 56:19.942
and it is gone into the
woods, just like that.

56:19.944 --> 56:21.777
I mean, pow!

56:21.779 --> 56:25.914
I mean... it... next morning,
I come out with my .22,

56:25.916 --> 56:28.984
