it off, you know?

56:28.986 --> 56:32.388
I look around, not too
far... about a couple

56:32.390 --> 56:35.391
hundred yards beyond
the room for our house.

56:35.393 --> 56:37.659
Lion's there.

56:37.661 --> 56:39.161
Dead.

56:39.163 --> 56:44.133
And it's, uh, its cub is trying
to suckle at it, you know?

56:44.135 --> 56:46.668
Get the last bit of milk.

56:46.670 --> 56:50.739
I come up too close to it, and
it stops, and kind of looks

56:50.741 --> 56:53.976
