57:05.655 --> 57:08.490
But then I'm walking home,
and I'm thinking, well,

57:08.492 --> 57:11.794
Misty didn't suffer.

57:11.796 --> 57:14.163
She's here, and then she's
gone, and the mountain lion

57:14.165 --> 57:15.464
didn't suffer.

57:15.466 --> 57:17.599
