pain, and died.

57:17.601 --> 57:21.403
But me and the cub,
we suffered the most,

57:21.405 --> 57:23.365
because we had to
carry that with us.

57:25.942 --> 57:30.379
What I do isn't about
the people that die.

57:30.381 --> 57:33.715
It's about the people
that are left alive.

57:33.717 --> 57:38.687
They get the short end of the
stick, as far as I'm concerned.

57:38.689 --> 57:42.324
Some of them are
blindsided, and some of them

57:42.326 --> 57:43.926
think the ends
justify the means.

57:43.928 --> 57:49.198
But there ain't no ends,
as long as there's people.

57:49.200 --> 57:51.166
They go on.

57:51.168 --> 57:52.501
It just doesn't matter.

57:55.338 --> 57:57.206
- Yeah, well I think that...

57:57.208 --> 57:59.168
- I don't give a
shit what you think.

58:02.479 --> 58:05.247
