59:18.389 --> 59:20.422
- Why'd you laugh, then?

59:20.424 --> 59:21.464
- Because it's funny.

59:28.031 --> 59:32.067
- So I guess you think
you're pretty funny, then.

59:32.069 --> 59:33.569
- Funnier than you.

59:33.571 --> 59:36.138
- Oh, yeah?

59:36.140 --> 59:36.900
- Yeah.

59:47.417 --> 59:49.351
Don't get my hair wet.

59:49.353 --> 59:50.113
- Sorry.

01:00:08.905 --> 01:00:10.405
Thought you were watching that?

01:00:10.407 --> 01:00:11.974
- No, it's stupid.

