Oh, hey... go back.

01:00:18.315 --> 01:00:19.114
I want to watch that.

01:00:19.116 --> 01:00:19.815
Hey, hey, hey.

01:00:19.817 --> 01:00:21.216
- No.

01:00:21.218 --> 01:00:22.551
You can't.

01:00:24.554 --> 01:00:25.394
- All right.

01:01:06.262 --> 01:01:07.362
- OK.

